Privacy Policy:
1.	Information Collection: We collect user phone numbers, full names, and device IDs for account management, personalization, and advertisement purposes. No user data is shared with third parties.
2.	Survey Participation: Users are encouraged to participate in surveys on environmental awareness and sustainability. All responses are valid and contribute to earning points.
3.	Data Security: We employ industry-standard measures to ensure the security of user data.
4.	Payment Information: Users' payment preferences are securely stored and used for payment processing at the end of each month.
5.	Communication: All communication regarding payment and account management will be conducted through the provided phone number.
6.	Ads: The app may contain ads from external sources. However, user data is not shared with these advertisers.
7.	App Management: EcoPulse Surveys is managed by Arrianah Investments Ltd. Contact us at axisgraphics1@gmail.com for any inquiries or support.
8.	Policy Changes: We reserve the right to update our Privacy Policy as needed. Users will be notified of any changes.
9.	User Rights: Users have the right to access, correct, or delete their personal information stored within the app.
10.	Data Retention: User data will be retained as long as necessary for the purposes outlined in this policy or as required by law.
